  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>TAV score and number of tachyarrhythmic events.</measure>
    <time_frame>The two phases M0 - M12 and M12 - M24 will be examined separately. For each 12 months period the TAV score at its beginning and tachyarrhythmic events in the following 12 months will be assessed. The NPV will be calculated for both phases.</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
